  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees.",
    "Slice the crusty bread into 1 inch thick slices.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together flour, egg, milk, sugar, and salt.",
    "Add the sliced bread to the bowl and toss until the bread is evenly coated.",
    "Heat the sesame oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the bread slices to the skillet and cook until golden brown.",
    "Transfer the bread to a baking sheet and bake for 10 minutes.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together chopped scallions and minced garlic.",
    "Sprinkle the scallion and garlic mixture over the bread.",
    "Serve the crispy kalguksu hot and enjoy."
